               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400302-name-323" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400302-name-323" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400302-name-323" type="surname" value="BALLARD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400302-name-323" type="given" value="ELIZA"></interp>ELIZA BALLARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Bishopsgate-street, and am assistant to Mr. William Ward, a hosier. On Saturday evening, the 8th of February, I was in the shop—the prisoner opened the shop-door, and took a piece of silk-handkerchiefs from the counter—he ran off—I called to Mr. Ward, and he ran after him—this is the piece of handkerchiefs—(<hi rend="italic">examining it</hi>)—it contains seven handkerchiefs, which are not divided.</p>
               <p>
