                  </hi>. I was in my shop on the 8th of February, about five o'clock in the evening—I ran out, and took the prisoner in Throgmorton-street—he had this piece of silk handkerchiefs on him, which are my pro<lb></lb>perty.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was in great distress, and had no meant of sup<lb></lb>porting myself.</p>
